Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:55.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,土壇場で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:55.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,首の皮１枚つながったカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:54.60,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji held on by the skin of\Nhis neck at the last moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:01:00.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼らが生還するためには
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:01:00.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと星４つが必要である
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:59.71,default,,0,0,0,,With his group, they now\Nneed four stars to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:03.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 手元には
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:03.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1400万の現金のみ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:05.46,default,,0,0,0,,But they only have 14 million\Nin cash and zero cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:05.46,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Failure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:06.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードは０
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:11.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当は３連勝の目も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:11.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あったんだけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:11.01,default,,0,0,0,,Actually, we could have won\Nthree straight though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.63,0:01:14.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星２つなら上等っすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:13.75,default,,0,0,0,,Two stars is\Nmore than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.54,0:01:16.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら ２人で分けろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:16.25,default,,0,0,0,,Here, split this up\Nbetween yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:18.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.46,0:01:18.25,default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:20.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰がつけても一緒なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:20.78,default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter\Nwho keeps them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ったろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３人で星を９個にするって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:24.26,default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I say before that\Nwe'll get nine stars altogether?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:28.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:28.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいの？カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.75,0:01:26.28,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.87,0:01:28.50,default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:31.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それより あと星４つ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:30.94,default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,\Nwe need four more stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:33.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやったら手に入れられるかだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:33.00,default,,0,0,0,,We have to think of\Nhow to get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:35.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやってって…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:35.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードがないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:35.01,default,,0,0,0,,How can we get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:37.51,default,,0,0,0,,Without any cards,\Nwe can only buy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:37.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星は買うしか…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:39.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 手持ちの金じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:42.32,default,,0,0,0,,No, with our money now,\Nit's impossible to buy all four.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:42.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とても星４つなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:42.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買えないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:44.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも… それじゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:44.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう どうやっても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.32,0:01:46.09,default,,0,0,0,,But, does this mean that\Nthere's no hope for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:46.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助からないってことですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:46.51,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:49.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星は買えない カードもなしじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:49.80,default,,0,0,0,,We can't buy stars,\Nand we haven't any cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:52.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時間切れを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:52.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待つしかないんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:52.25,default,,0,0,0,,Is all we can do to\Nwait for time to run out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:57.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードがない？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:57.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなもの どうにでもなるだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:56.09,default,,0,0,0,,Without any cards,\Nthere's still a way. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:02:01.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その辺の誰かからもらえば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:02:01.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだけの話じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:01.62,default,,0,0,0,,We can always get them\Nfrom someone over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:05.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もらえばって そんなこと…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:05.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:04.10,default,,0,0,0,,Get them? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:04.10,kaiji-overlap,,0,0,0,,What's going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:07.18,default,,0,0,0,,No! Forgive me this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:08.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む　見逃してくれ　頼むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:08.60,default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:11.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,静粛に 静粛に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:11.61,default,,0,0,0,,Silence! Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:14.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この男は今
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:14.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,トイレで余分なカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:17.41,default,,0,0,0,,This guy tried to flush\Nhis cards down the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:17.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,便器に捨て流した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:17.41,kaiji-overlap,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:19.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初に言ったはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:19.11,default,,0,0,0,,We warned you at the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:23.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう行為は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:23.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一切 認めていないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:22.62,default,,0,0,0,,Such behaviour\Nwill not be tolerated!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:26.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードを破棄することは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:26.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許されない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:26.69,default,,0,0,0,,Disposal of the cards\Nis not allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:30.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいな？破棄は一切 認めない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:30.10,default,,0,0,0,,Listen up!\NDisposal is not allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:32.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無条件で別室行きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:32.57,default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional ejection\Nto the other room!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:34.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不正行為は厳罰に処す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.69,default,,0,0,0,,Cheating will be met\Nwith severe punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:36.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆ… 許してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:39.21,default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!\NI'm sorry, I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:39.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪かった　謝るから…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:42.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:42.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり まずいっすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:40.27,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:41.94,default,,0,0,0,,It's a bad idea, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:45.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードは自分で使い切らなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:45.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメなんです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:45.10,default,,0,0,0,,The only way is to\Nuse your own cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:47.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かから もらうだなんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.52,default,,0,0,0,,It's against the rules\Nto get cards from others...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:51.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 本気で言ってんのかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:50.21,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.\NDo you really believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:55.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この船は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:55.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードの譲渡は認めている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:54.97,default,,0,0,0,,The transfer of cards is allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:57.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:56.72,default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:03:00.95,default,,0,0,0,,Aren't the cards and stars\Nbeing shared among us right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:03:02.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,現に俺たちの間で カードも星も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:03:02.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行き来してるじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:06.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒服のやつらが俺たちの行為に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:06.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気づいてないと思うか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:06.19,default,,0,0,0,,Do you think those black suits\Ndon't know what we're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:08.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり認めてんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:08.30,default,,0,0,0,,In other words, this is allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:11.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破棄はダメだが譲渡はいいと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.96,default,,0,0,0,,Disposal is prohibited,\Nbut transfer is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:15.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この限定ジャンケン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:15.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一見 運否天賦に見えるが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:15.20,default,,0,0,0,,At first, this game of Restricted\NRock Paper Scissors might seem...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:20.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その本質は恐らく気づきのゲーム
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:20.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気づき？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:18.87,default,,0,0,0,,...like a game of chance,\Nbut it's really about awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:20.37,default,,0,0,0,,Awareness?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:23.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのことに気づかなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:23.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきの男みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:24.03,default,,0,0,0,,If unaware of that,\Nyou'd end up like that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:27.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自ら奈落に落ちることもあり得る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:26.26,default,,0,0,0,,...and fall out of\Nyour own doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:29.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一筋縄じゃいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:29.14,default,,0,0,0,,Ordinary methods don't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:32.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見かけよりずっと複雑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.62,default,,0,0,0,,This is more complicated\Nthan it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:35.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実は思考の勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.35,default,,0,0,0,,It's really a game of wits!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:37.89,default,,0,0,0,,Behind this game's\Nofficial rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:37.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このゲームは表のルールに対して
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:40.36,default,,0,0,0,,there's another set\Nof hidden rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:41.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,裏にひそむ もう１つのルールが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:41.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隠されている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:45.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちはグループを組んだことで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:45.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つ裏のルールを探し当てた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:45.16,default,,0,0,0,,By forming a group,\Nwe discovered one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだそのことに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がついていない者が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:48.11,default,,0,0,0,,There are still many\Non this floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:50.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このフロアには
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:50.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たくさんいるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:49.87,default,,0,0,0,,...who have yet to realise this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:54.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その真意に気づいた今なら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:54.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちにもチャンスはある
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:54.37,default,,0,0,0,,For us who have realised it,\Nthere's still a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:04:00.68,default,,0,0,0,,The game quickly drew\Nnearer to its conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:58.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急速に場は煮詰まりつつあった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:01.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終局に向かって…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:03.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,103名いたプレーヤーのうち
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:06.18,default,,0,0,0,,Out of the 104 players,\N33 have had their results.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:06.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すでに33名の決着がついた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:11.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,主催者側の余った星の買い取り
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:11.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,という戦略もあいまって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:11.22,default,,0,0,0,,With the organisers\Nbuying up the extra stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星３個以上で２階に上がった者が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すでに25人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:13.62,default,,0,0,0,,25 people with three stars\Nor more have already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:14.66,default,,0,0,0,,...ascended to the 2nd floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:18.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星を３つ失い
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:18.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別室へ落ちた者は８人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:18.66,default,,0,0,0,,Eight lost all their three stars\Nand went to the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:23.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり このフロアに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:23.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残っているのは 70人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:22.53,default,,0,0,0,,In other words, 70 players\Nstill remain on this floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:26.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして カードの総数は389枚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:26.91,default,,0,0,0,,The total number\Nof cards left is 389.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星は197個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.83,default,,0,0,0,,There are 197 remaining stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:32.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人当たりに直せば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:32.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カード5.55枚で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:34.41,default,,0,0,0,,This tallies to 5.55 cards\Nand 2.81 stars per person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:34.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星2.81個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:37.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり この中の何人かは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:39.39,default,,0,0,0,,Thus, some here would definitely\Nproceed to the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確実に別室行きとなる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:47.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 早くカードを集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:47.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負しましょうよ カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:47.01,default,,0,0,0,,Then let's hurry and\Ncollect cards to duel, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:50.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:50.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただやみくもに勝負はできない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:50.43,default,,0,0,0,,No. We can't do this blindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:54.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 何か手を打たないと…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:54.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.93,default,,0,0,0,,But we have to do something !
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:53.93,default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:57.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か勝つ方法があるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:57.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:57.93,default,,0,0,0,,There must be some way\Nto win! Some way…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:01.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ もう…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:01.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２時間 切ってるんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:01.44,default,,0,0,0,,But two hours\Nhave already passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:15.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:18.21,default,,0,0,0,,That's it. If we can't get stars,\Nwe can get cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:19.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星はダメでもカードは手に入る
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:19.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:18.82,default,,0,0,0,,The cards…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.32,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:22.16,default,,0,0,0,,We can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つけた　究極の必勝法！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:24.16,default,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.46,default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate winning strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:30.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それって どういうことですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.23,default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:32.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たとえばの話だが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:35.80,default,,0,0,0,,For example, we get a relatively\Nlarge number of Rock cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:36.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちがグーのカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:36.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相当数 手に入れていたとする
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で どう考える？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:39.07,default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you make of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:41.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうって…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.51,default,,0,0,0,,What do I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 無理もない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:43.47,default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:47.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 今から１時間30分が過ぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.55,default,,0,0,0,,What if in an hour\Nand a half from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:50.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このカードバランスのまま
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:50.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100の位が消え
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:50.56,default,,0,0,0,,the total number of cards\Nin the deck mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:54.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10の位だけという状況になったら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:52.83,default,,0,0,0,,...fell to two\Ninstead of three digits?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その時 俺たちがグーを
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,30枚 持っていたらどう思う？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:58.44,default,,0,0,0,,What do you suppose\Nif we have 30 Rock cards then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:01.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ 圧勝じゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:01.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.49,default,,0,0,0,,We'd win hands down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:01.56,default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:02.30,default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:06.07,default,,0,0,0,,Well, in reality, it wouldn't\Ngo that smoothly but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:06.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 現実的には
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:06.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこまでにはならないだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:10.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ確率は飛躍的に上がるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:09.20,default,,0,0,0,,...the probability of winning\Nwould be raised considerably.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:13.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑　安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.04,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata, Ando!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グーだ　グーを30枚 かき集めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:16.38,default,,0,0,0,,Rocks!\NCollect 30 Rock cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:19.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,30枚ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:19.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.75,default,,0,0,0,,30 cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:19.54,default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.38,default,,0,0,0,,How do we get such a\Nlarge number of cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:22.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけのカード
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:22.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやって集めるんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:23.88,default,,0,0,0,,Use cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:29.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金を使う　グー１枚につき
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:29.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10万使おうと20万使おうと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:28.39,default,,0,0,0,,Paying 10,000 or 20,000\Nfor a Rock card...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:33.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それがのちのち
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:33.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星に化けると考えれば安いもの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:30.47,default,,0,0,0,,...makes no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.88,default,,0,0,0,,Considering how they'd\Nearn us stars later, it's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:35.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先行投資だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.39,default,,0,0,0,,It's a mere investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:40.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の状況 考えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:40.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渋ってる時じゃねえ　分かるな？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:38.40,default,,0,0,0,,Looking at our situation now,\Nthere's no time to hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:39.73,default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:43.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい 分かります
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:43.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,異存はありません
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.93,default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.23,default,,0,0,0,,No objections!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:47.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせ俺たちの200万じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:47.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星は買えないし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:47.07,default,,0,0,0,,We can't buy any stars\Nwith our two million anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:49.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部 つぎ込んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:49.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悔いはありません
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:49.59,default,,0,0,0,,There nothing to regret\Neven if we use it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:52.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:52.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ早速…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.61,default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:52.06,default,,0,0,0,,Right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:53.18,default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:55.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て　どこ行く気だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:54.40,default,,0,0,0,,Where do you\Nthink you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:57.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちが動いてどうすんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.68,default,,0,0,0,,Why are we doing this\Nby ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:58.72,default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:00.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:05.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか？この買い占めは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:05.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気づかれたら終わりなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:04.26,default,,0,0,0,,Listen, if word of this hoarding\Ngets out, it's over for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:08.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バレちゃ誰１人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:08.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負なんかしてくれなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:07.99,default,,0,0,0,,If others know of it,\Nno one would challenge us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:10.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも カードを手に入れないと…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.69,default,,0,0,0,,But, we have to get the cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:14.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,資金はあるんだ　人を使おう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:13.44,default,,0,0,0,,We have the funds.\NLet's use other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星の多いやつは多いやつで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:16.00,default,,0,0,0,,Those with more stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:18.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードの譲渡は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:18.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽じゃないはずだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.44,default,,0,0,0,,...wouldn't be able to\Ntransfer their cards easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:22.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星の足らない連中から見れば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:22.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このフロアから これ以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:22.64,default,,0,0,0,,And those on this floor\Nwithout enough stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:26.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星の数を減らしたくないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:26.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,共通の思いのはず
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:25.44,default,,0,0,0,,...should want to retain them\Nto avoid disappearing from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:29.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから星４つ以上のやつはダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:28.73,default,,0,0,0,,So those with four stars\Nor more are out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:33.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星３つのやつを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:33.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちの工作員に仕立て上げる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:32.38,default,,0,0,0,,Make those with\Nthree stars our agents!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:36.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グーのカードを10枚以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:36.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,集めてきたら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:36.54,default,,0,0,0,,The plan was such that\Nthose with 10 or more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:39.41,default,,0,0,0,,...Rock cards would have\Ntheir decks taken from them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:39.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手持ちのカードを全部もらい受け
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:39.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:42.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,報酬200万を渡すという提案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:41.46,default,,0,0,0,,with a reward of two million.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:46.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結果的にこれがヒット
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:46.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,抜けた発想だった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:44.22,default,,0,0,0,,And it was a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:45.46,default,,0,0,0,,It was a genius idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:50.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにこれは代行者にとって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:50.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リスク抜きでカードを始末でき
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:50.85,default,,0,0,0,,The other party could get rid\Nof their cards at little risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:54.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かつ200万の金を手にして
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:54.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,上がることができるという
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:54.63,default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, a tidy sum of\Ntwo million could be made.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:56.44,default,,0,0,0,,An appetising deal, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいしい話である
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:08:00.44,default,,0,0,0,,For Kaiji and gang,\Nby using these agents,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:08:00.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジらにとっても
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:08:00.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,代行してもらうことで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:04.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秘密裏に必要なだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:04.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グーを手に入れることができる上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:04.37,default,,0,0,0,,they can get the cards they need\Nwithout being exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:07.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,代行者たちは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:07.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕事が終わると報酬をもらい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:07.76,default,,0,0,0,,Once the agents\Nhave done their jobs,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,上に上がってしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:09.22,default,,0,0,0,,they rise up\Nto the next level.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:12.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,永遠にこのフロアから消える
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:12.10,default,,0,0,0,,And are gone\Nfrom this floor forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:14.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべてが理想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.46,default,,0,0,0,,It was a perfect plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジらはついに手に入れた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.84,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and gang\Nhad finally got...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:20.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命運を賭けた最終戦略
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:19.46,default,,0,0,0,,...the final strategy\Nto bet their destiny on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:23.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その実弾　グーのカード30枚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.96,default,,0,0,0,,And an ammunition of\N30 Rock cards to back it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:29.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,注ぎ込んだカイジらの資金は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:29.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑 安藤の
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:29.88,default,,0,0,0,,The funds that Kaiji,\NFuruhata and Ando...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全財産を合わせて800万円
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:32.21,default,,0,0,0,,...used in total\Nwas eight million.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:35.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう あとには戻れない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.03,default,,0,0,0,,There's no turning back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:38.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑　安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:38.21,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata, Ando.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:41.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,快感だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:39.61,default,,0,0,0,,This feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:45.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちはこの限定ジャンケンの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:45.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,構造に手を突っ込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:45.16,default,,0,0,0,,We have delved into\Nthe inner dynamics...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:49.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,操作し得るってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:49.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちがこの世界を！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.22,default,,0,0,0,,...of this Restricted\NRock Scissors Paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.39,default,,0,0,0,,We can rule this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:50.89,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:52.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:56.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,震えるぜ　大仕掛けに胸が震える
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.89,default,,0,0,0,,I'm shaking in anticipation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.58,default,,0,0,0,,This plan is filling me\Nwith anticipation…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:00.90,default,,0,0,0,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:04.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さてと　仕事はまだやっと半分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:04.12,default,,0,0,0,,We have halfway more to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,難しいのは むしろこれからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:06.91,default,,0,0,0,,This is the difficult part.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:11.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジはこの戦略を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:11.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑 安藤に語る
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:11.20,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji explains the plan\Nto Furuhata and Ando,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:15.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 仕掛けを打つ頃合い
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:15.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,方法を伝える
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:14.91,default,,0,0,0,,and how to set up the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:20.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし機を逸すれば 致命的な敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:18.57,default,,0,0,0,,Missing a beat\Nwould result in a fatal blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:22.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫　必ずうまくいく
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:22.66,default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry,\Nit will surely go well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:26.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たち３人で星10個も夢じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:25.44,default,,0,0,0,,It's not impossible even\Nfor us to get ten stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:31.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 12個13個も…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:31.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:29.08,default,,0,0,0,,No, even 12 or 13 is possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.40,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船で借りた金と
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その金利をきれいにしても
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.59,default,,0,0,0,,Even if we clear all our debts,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:36.17,default,,0,0,0,,we'll have a profit\Nof seven million each!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:37.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人頭700万以上 浮く
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.21,default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a sweep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:39.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大勝だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:44.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは必ず大金を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:44.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この船を降りることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:44.44,default,,0,0,0,,We can definitely\Nleave this ship rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:47.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.68,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:49.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やり直そうな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.05,default,,0,0,0,,Let's start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:53.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし首尾よく大勝して
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:53.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この船を降りられたら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:53.28,default,,0,0,0,,If we can get off\Nthis ship victorious,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:57.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺もお前らもやり直そう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:56.05,default,,0,0,0,,let us all\Nstart our lives afresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:10:00.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今までのような
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:10:00.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よどんだ くぐもった…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.06,default,,0,0,0,,Let's escape the\Nstagnant daily life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなはっきりしない毎日から
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,抜け出して
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:03.56,default,,0,0,0,,...that we were\Nswimming in till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:07.06,default,,0,0,0,,What should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:11.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何て言うか…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:11.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと価値のある暮らし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.60,default,,0,0,0,,Let's live a life\Nof higher value.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:14.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うまく言えねえが ともかく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:14.07,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know\Nhow to say it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:18.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今までと まるで違う人生を
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:18.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,漕ぎ出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:17.11,default,,0,0,0,,...let's lead different lives\Nfrom this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:23.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度こそ３人で力を合わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:22.08,default,,0,0,0,,This time,\Nlet's give it our all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:27.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張ります！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:27.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お 俺も
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.64,default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:26.08,default,,0,0,0,,M-Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:29.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やり直そう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:30.58,default,,0,0,0,,Let's reset everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:32.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべてを
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:36.76,default,,0,0,0,,Ten cards each.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10枚ずつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:40.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あくまでチームプレーだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:40.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かるな？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.94,default,,0,0,0,,But remember that\Nthis is team work, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:43.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:43.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの… カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:40.76,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:42.80,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:46.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グー30枚はともかく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:50.31,default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it unsafe just to have two\NScissors and four Paper cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:48.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキ２枚 パー４枚ってのは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少し心もとなくないですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買い足しておいたほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいんじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:53.14,default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we buy a few more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:56.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや やめとこう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.41,default,,0,0,0,,No, let's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.76,default,,0,0,0,,Let's avoid anything\Nthat will raise suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:11:00.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怪しまれそうな動きは一切 よそう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:11:00.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:10:59.42,default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:02.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ チェックに行ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:02.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.42,default,,0,0,0,,Alright, go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:02.64,default,,0,0,0,,Ando.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.42,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:05.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 行ってまいります
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:07.70,default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい　出る時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いちいち断ったりなんかするな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:11.43,default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't talk to us\Neverytime you go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人に見られたらどうする
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:13.69,default,,0,0,0,,What would we do\Nif someone saw us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:16.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:14.91,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:17.46,default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:19.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ったく
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:22.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっと… タバコはまずいよな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:22.07,default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I can't smoke here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:24.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここには誰もいないことに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:24.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なってるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.67,default,,0,0,0,,No one is supposed be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:33.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジたちは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:33.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,交代で残り枚数を見張る
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:32.95,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and gang took turns to\Nmonitor the number of cards left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:37.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕掛けを打つ理想的状況の出現を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:37.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ちながら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:37.42,default,,0,0,0,,They waited for the ideal moment\Nto set up their game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:40.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５分して安藤が戻ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:43.66,default,,0,0,0,,In five minutes, Ando returned\Nand Furuhata went in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:44.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次に古畑がチェックに向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードの推移は順調
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.16,default,,0,0,0,,The movement of the cards\Nwent smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:49.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし この時 カイジの心中に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:49.69,default,,0,0,0,,But at this moment,\Na strange feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:52.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ある違和感が生まれつつあった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:51.40,default,,0,0,0,,...began to surface\Nin Kaiji's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:55.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは 正体の見えない危機感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.90,default,,0,0,0,,It was a sense of impending\Ncrisis that he couldn't identify.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:12:00.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,原因は分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:12:00.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 確かにカイジは感じていた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:57.35,default,,0,0,0,,He had no idea why.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.91,default,,0,0,0,,But Kaiji could feel it growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:03.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ある変調の兆しを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:02.69,default,,0,0,0,,A sense of impending doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:14.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやらカードの買い占めに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:14.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動いている者がいるようです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:14.15,default,,0,0,0,,Seems like there are some\Nwho are buying out cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.62,default,,0,0,0,,Buying out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:16.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買い占めか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:21.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで限定ジャンケンの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:21.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,裏をかいたつもりなんでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:20.44,default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps they think that\Nthey have beaten the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:25.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一時の錯覚とも知らずに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:25.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愚かなことよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:25.90,default,,0,0,0,,How foolish of them not to know\Nthat it's just a temporal illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:31.14,default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:33.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,順調じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:33.24,default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it going smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:36.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,順調に推移している
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.78,default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:39.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も恐れることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:38.93,default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:41.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不安がることはないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:40.78,default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:46.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:46.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:45.28,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:46.35,default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か… 何か変なんです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.86,default,,0,0,0,,Something...\NSomething's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:57.33,default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:13:00.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな… なぜチョキが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:13:00.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなに早く減っていくんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:00.33,default,,0,0,0,,Why are the Scissors\Ndecreasing so rapidly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:02.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままパーのカードより
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:04.62,default,,0,0,0,,If the Scissors cards decrease\Nfaster than the Paper ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:04.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキのカードが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:04.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,減ることになると
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの戦略は破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:06.34,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's plan would fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:10.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　ここが限界です
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:10.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負に行きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.31,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!\NWe can't wait any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:10.75,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go out and duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:14.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:11.95,default,,0,0,0,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:18.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは耐えるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:18.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと言ってるうちに…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.35,default,,0,0,0,,We must wait this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.60,default,,0,0,0,,But while you say that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:22.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耐えるんだ　目先を追うな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.67,default,,0,0,0,,Bear with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.17,default,,0,0,0,,Don't think only short term!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:25.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちはいつもそれで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:25.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失敗してきたんじゃないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:25.46,default,,0,0,0,,Haven't we always failed\Nbecause of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:28.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は耐えろ　そして信じるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:28.46,default,,0,0,0,,Bear with it for now,\Nand have confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:32.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず反転する
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:32.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは単なる勘じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:30.71,default,,0,0,0,,This will surely turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:32.46,default,,0,0,0,,This is not just any feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:36.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキが減ったってことは パーが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:36.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使いやすくなったってことで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:36.51,default,,0,0,0,,With Scissors decreasing,\NPaper becomes easier to use,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:39.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ずここからは使われていく
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:39.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆にチョキは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:38.47,default,,0,0,0,,and will decrease\Nfrom here on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.78,default,,0,0,0,,Conversely, it's hard\Nto use Scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:42.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グーがあまりカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:42.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,減らさないから使いにくい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.47,default,,0,0,0,,...with many Rocks out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:46.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ だからパーが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:46.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動かなかったんすね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.98,default,,0,0,0,,No wonder the number\Nof Papers are stagnant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:49.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 買い占めをしてた頃から
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.04,default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:50.98,default,,0,0,0,,No, I just noticed when\NI was out buying cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:51.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと気になってたんす
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しパーの減りが少ないなって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.74,default,,0,0,0,,The number of Papers didn't\Nseem to be decreasing by a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:56.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも あの時は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:56.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキが多かったから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:58.14,default,,0,0,0,,But that was due to\Nmany Scissors at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:14:01.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パーの減りも少なかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:14:01.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうことなんすね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:13:59.49,default,,0,0,0,,That's the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:04.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貼りついたように動かぬパー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.49,default,,0,0,0,,The Paper cards that\Nare not moving at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:05.50,default,,0,0,0,,Scissors again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:07.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,またチョキが…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:07.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耐えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:06.90,default,,0,0,0,,Bear with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:09.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは分かるんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:11.50,default,,0,0,0,,I know, but why are the Scissors\Ndisappearing two at a time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしてチョキは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚ずつ減るんです？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:15.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２つずつ その数を減らすチョキ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:15.50,default,,0,0,0,,The Scissors that are\Ndisappearing in pairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.77,default,,0,0,0,,The rest are decreasing\None by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:17.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかのは１枚ずつ 消えていくのに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:19.97,default,,0,0,0,,but Scissors are\Ndecreasing in pairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:21.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキは２つずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:21.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消えていくんです　ね？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:20.80,default,,0,0,0,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:24.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その２つの符号が意味するもの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:24.51,default,,0,0,0,,What these two factors\Nindicate, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:35.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やられた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:35.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちだけじゃなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:33.16,default,,0,0,0,,We've been caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:35.62,default,,0,0,0,,It's not just us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:38.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:38.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたんですか 一体？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:38.63,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, what exactly is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:42.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買い占めだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:42.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かがパーを買い占めた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.17,default,,0,0,0,,Hoarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:43.01,default,,0,0,0,,Someone is hoarding\NPaper cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:43.77,default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:47.47,default,,0,0,0,,It must be that someone's\Nhoarding the cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:47.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かが買い占めてると
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:47.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えるしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:51.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから チョキが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:51.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２つずつ 消えていく
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:50.57,default,,0,0,0,,That's why the Scissors\Nare disappearing in pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいこでつぶし合うから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:52.97,default,,0,0,0,,They are eliminated\Nby drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:57.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ このままだと…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:56.48,default,,0,0,0,,S-So, at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:15:00.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうにかならないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:15:00.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:59.48,default,,0,0,0,,Is there something\Nwe can do, Kaiji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:02.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうにもならない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:01.55,default,,0,0,0,,There's no way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべては破綻した
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.49,default,,0,0,0,,Everything is falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:14.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは カイジが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:14.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生まれて初めて味わう恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:13.69,default,,0,0,0,,That was the first time Kaiji\Nexperienced that sort of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:17.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこまでも降下していく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:17.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この感覚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:17.50,default,,0,0,0,,The feeling of falling\Nto infinite depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:26.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:26.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:24.80,default,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:29.22,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! Kaiji! Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:29.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん… カイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:38.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,う… 動くなら今しかない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.83,default,,0,0,0,,We have to move now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:41.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グーがクズカードになる前に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:41.32,default,,0,0,0,,Before the Rock cards\Nbecome useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふ… 古畑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.36,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.37,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:47.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:47.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:53.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 カイジにも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:53.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この今しかないという思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:55.19,default,,0,0,0,,Of course it was hard for Kaiji\Nto curb the urge of impulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,抑えがたく押し寄せる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:59.34,default,,0,0,0,,It surged forward,\Nforward, forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:59.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,押し寄せる　押し寄せる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:02.84,default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:04.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て！止まれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:08.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破滅へと誘う
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:08.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブルという魔物の触手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:08.01,default,,0,0,0,,The demon of gambling drew\Nthem closer to destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:12.18,default,,0,0,0,,The tenacious hand of\Nthat demon burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:12.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その粘りついた手は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:12.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,焼けるように熱く
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:16.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,幾重にも絡みつき
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:16.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,容易には離れない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:15.55,default,,0,0,0,,Once preyed upon,\Nit is difficult to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:20.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本人は自分で考え
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:20.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行動しているつもりだが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:20.06,default,,0,0,0,,One may believe he is\Nacting of his own free will,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:24.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実は もうすっかり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:24.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔物に操られている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:24.10,default,,0,0,0,,but he is actually\Ncontrolled by that demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:29.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑も安藤もこの戦略に費やした
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:29.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,労力 金が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:28.48,default,,0,0,0,,Neither Furuhata nor Ando\Ncould withstand its hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:32.38,default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't bear the effort and\Nmoney they put into this plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,惜しくて惜しくてたまらない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:36.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この戦略が無為に終わることなど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:36.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことは許せない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:34.41,default,,0,0,0,,simply go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.42,default,,0,0,0,,That could not be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:38.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あってはならぬこと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:38.10,default,,0,0,0,,They would not allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:42.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チェック　セット
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:39.41,default,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:42.68,default,,0,0,0,,Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:45.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む　せめて１勝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:45.18,default,,0,0,0,,Please, give me\None win at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:49.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:46.92,default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.98,default,,0,0,0,,Why must it turn\Nout to be Paper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:52.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よりによって ここでパーかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.56,default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:54.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やりー
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:58.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 古畑 安藤　共に返り討ち
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:58.13,default,,0,0,0,,At the end, both\NFuruhata and Ando lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３人でまた星３つ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:04.10,default,,0,0,0,,The three of them are\Ndown to three stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:06.57,default,,0,0,0,,less than what\Nthey started with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:07.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当初の状況に逆戻り
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:10.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,増えたのは ただ絶望のみ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:10.18,default,,0,0,0,,What increased was\Nmerely their despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:13.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう戦略もくそもねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:13.13,default,,0,0,0,,There's no more strategy left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:16.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やみくもに戦うしか道はねえのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:16.58,default,,0,0,0,,Is our only hope to\Nplay blindly from here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:23.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が悪知恵の首謀者か
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:23.59,default,,0,0,0,,So you're the\Nmastermind behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:26.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあピンと来るかな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:26.26,default,,0,0,0,,Then you should\Nprobably guess who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:30.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ その後ろにいるやつ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:33.03,default,,0,0,0,,That guy behind him\Nchallenged me just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっき俺と勝負したやつっすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も… その後ろのやつ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.06,default,,0,0,0,,Me too, with that guy behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:36.75,default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:39.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど　俺たちは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:39.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狙い撃ちされたってことか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.17,default,,0,0,0,,We were being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:42.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつらだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:44.47,default,,0,0,0,,These are the guys who\Nhoarded the Paper cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:46.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パーを買い占めた連中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:49.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすが首謀者 察しがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:48.98,default,,0,0,0,,As expected of the\Nmastermind, you're sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:52.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに悪い戦略じゃないもんな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:52.55,default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a bad plan, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし俺たちがいなかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:57.20,default,,0,0,0,,If we weren't here,\Nyou might have succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:58.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今頃 成功していたかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:02.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実はその戦略
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:02.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちもやろうと思ってたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:01.99,default,,0,0,0,,We actually thought\Nof that same plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,というより
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実際 動き出してみたら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:04.85,default,,0,0,0,,But when we were about\Nto follow through,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:08.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうも俺たち以外にグーを
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:08.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買い占めてるやつらがいることに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:10.50,default,,0,0,0,,we heard about people\Nbuying up Rock cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:10.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がついたってことさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:17.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で 急遽 予定変更
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:17.14,default,,0,0,0,,So, we changed our tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:22.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グーを捨て
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:22.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちはパーを買い占めた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:21.08,default,,0,0,0,,Instead of Rock, we bought Paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:26.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思ったとおり…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:26.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで踊ってくれると痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:26.45,default,,0,0,0,,And it sure feels great\Nto think that it worked so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:31.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感謝するよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:31.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らの浅知恵と軽率な行動に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:31.25,default,,0,0,0,,I'm thankful to your\Nshallow wisdom and rashness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:35.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何の用だ？まさかその自慢話を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:35.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しに来たわけじゃあるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:33.22,default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:35.99,default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you came here\Njust to show off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:40.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　用はある
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.73,default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, there's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:44.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も俺も同じ戦略を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:44.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思いついた者同士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:44.02,default,,0,0,0,,You thought of the\Nsame strategy as I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うなら好敵手ってやつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:46.47,default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nyou're a worthy rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:49.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,似てんだよ お前と俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:49.40,default,,0,0,0,,We are alike, you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:53.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 １枚俺が上回り
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:53.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パー派の勝ちとなったが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:53.65,default,,0,0,0,,Although Paper\Nwill win at the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:56.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実力は伯仲していた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:56.01,default,,0,0,0,,our abilities are on par.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:19:01.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこそ お前は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:19:01.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちの最後にふさわしい男
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:19:00.88,default,,0,0,0,,So, you are ideal for us\Nto play our last match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:02.52,default,,0,0,0,,Last match?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:04.11,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:06.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前との戦いが最後だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:06.34,default,,0,0,0,,Our match with you is our last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:09.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは勝っても負けても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:09.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２階へ上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:09.46,default,,0,0,0,,Win or lose, we're advancing\Nto the second level.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:13.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間 程ってのが肝心よ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:13.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいキリだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:13.80,default,,0,0,0,,A person needs\Nto know his limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:18.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とはいえ お前も星１つじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:18.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦うに戦えまい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:17.75,default,,0,0,0,,Even with your battle wits,\Nyou can't fight with one star.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:21.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで まず俺たちの星を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:21.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つ 売ってやる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:21.53,default,,0,0,0,,So, let us sell you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:25.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:25.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… あの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:22.79,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:27.47,default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, how much is it\Nfor the star?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:29.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくらなんですか 星？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:30.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.48,default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:33.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:33.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな強突く張りじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:33.48,default,,0,0,0,,We are not that greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:38.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船側の星の買い取り額に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:38.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100 上乗せするだけでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:35.92,default,,0,0,0,,Just one million\Nabove the price...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:38.48,default,,0,0,0,,...that the organisers\Nare buying stars for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:43.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,500万だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:41.39,default,,0,0,0,,Five million!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:47.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しゃくに障るけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:47.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この状況じゃ仕方ないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:47.53,default,,0,0,0,,This feels bad, but I guess\Nit's the only way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:49.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:48.66,default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:52.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰が星なんか買うかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.76,default,,0,0,0,,Who would buy your stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:54.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ？どうして…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:56.88,default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Unless we buy,\Nwe can't play anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:56.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 買っとかないと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:56.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負にも行けないし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:58.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お断りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:57.77,default,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:19:59.88,default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:02.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:02.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは別に構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:04.51,default,,0,0,0,,It's fine by us.\NWe'll find someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:05.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかを当たるまでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:05.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:05.95,default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:11.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て　星は買わねえが勝負はやる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.01,default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:10.75,default,,0,0,0,,I won't buy any stars\Nbut I will challenge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:14.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジさん　もし負けたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:14.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.58,default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiji! If you lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:14.52,default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:17.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな時は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:17.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっさり散りゃいいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:16.59,default,,0,0,0,,We'll face that when it happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:20.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この状況で何 言ってやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:20.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:18.96,default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:20.09,default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買い占め戦略に賭けた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にしてみれば
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:23.33,default,,0,0,0,,To play against and be\Ndefeated by the mastermind...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:27.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パー買い占め派の首謀者と
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:27.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やり合って散るなら本望だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:27.33,default,,0,0,0,,...behind the Paper hoarding\Nscheme is perfect for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:30.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつの言うとおり
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:32.34,default,,0,0,0,,Like he said, this is\Nan ideal last match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:32.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちにふさわしい最終戦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:36.81,default,,0,0,0,,However, it will be\Na death match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:39.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし… デスマッチだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:39.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,デスマッチ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.42,default,,0,0,0,,Death match?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:43.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:43.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっちかが完全に星を吐き出し
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.79,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:43.25,default,,0,0,0,,We'll play till either side\Nloses all his stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:45.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どちらかが別室へ行くまでやる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:45.05,default,,0,0,0,,And that party goes\Nto the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:47.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろ？茶髪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:47.49,default,,0,0,0,,Is that fine,\Nbrown-haired one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:50.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカが… 何 言ってやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:48.97,default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:50.78,default,,0,0,0,,What is he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:53.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が受けるわけ ねえじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:53.06,default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'll do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:56.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しは頭が回るやつかと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:56.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思ってたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:56.14,default,,0,0,0,,And I thought he was\Npretty smart too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:58.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,がっかりだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:20:57.42,default,,0,0,0,,What a letdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:06.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,トチ狂いやがって　クズが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:05.07,default,,0,0,0,,He's gone stark, raving mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:09.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは一縷の望みに賭け
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:12.07,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji bets his last hope on\Na last match with Kitami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:12.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,北見に最後の勝負を挑む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:17.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ち受けるのは生還か死か
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:14.07,default,,0,0,0,,What would be his fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.59,0:21:17.08,default,,0,0,0,,Life, or death?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.54,0:22:46.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次回｢決死｣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:45.92,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Deadly Decision.
